@AllByMyshelf.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7208

# Paste your Auth0 access token below (get it from the Angular app's Network tab)
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### Health check (no auth required)
GET {{AllByMyshelf.Api_HostAddress}}/health

###

### Releases
GET {{AllByMyshelf.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/releases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Books
GET {{AllByMyshelf.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sync status
GET {{AllByMyshelf.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/sync/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Collection value
GET {{AllByMyshelf.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/collection-value
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
